## Phase 2: AI & Cloud Pro Subscription (Future Update)

> [!WARNING]
> **Phase 2 is a significant engineering effort.** It introduces authentication, a cloud database, and AI integration. Do NOT start Phase 2 until Phase 1 is live and generating revenue. Phase 1 can ship independently.

### New Dependencies (Phase 2)

```
npm install @clerk/clerk-expo convex react-native-mmkv
```

