### Proposed Changes (Phase 2)

#### Convex Backend

##### [NEW] convex/schema.ts

Define the cloud database schema mirroring local types:

```typescript
// Tables: users, workouts, exerciseLogs, sets, personalRecords, bodyMeasurements
// All linked to userId from Clerk
```

##### [NEW] convex/workouts.ts

Convex queries and mutations:
- `list` вҖ” Get all workouts for authenticated user
- `create` вҖ” Save a workout
- `bulkImport` вҖ” One-time migration of local data to cloud

##### [NEW] convex/ai.ts

Convex Action that:
1. Receives the user's question
2. Runs `runQuery()` to fetch relevant workout data from the Convex DB
3. Builds a prompt with the user's data as context
4. Calls OpenAI API (key stored securely as Convex env var)
5. Returns the AI's response

#### App Changes (Phase 2)

##### [NEW] src/screens/AuthScreen.tsx

Sign-in screen using Clerk (Google + Apple Sign-In buttons). Only shown when user taps "Upgrade to AI Pro."

##### [NEW] src/screens/AIChatScreen.tsx

Chat interface for the AI Coach:
- Message bubbles (user = right, AI = left)
- Suggested questions ("Why is my bench stuck?", "What muscle am I neglecting?")
- Loading/streaming animation while AI responds
- Locked behind Tier 3 paywall

##### [NEW] src/services/dataMigration.ts

The "Great Merge" service:
1. Reads all local AsyncStorage data
2. Calls `bulkImport` Convex mutation to upload to cloud
3. Marks migration as complete in local storage
4. Future reads/writes go to Convex instead of AsyncStorage

##### [MODIFY] src/context/SubscriptionContext.tsx

Extend to support the `ai_pro` tier:
- Check RevenueCat for active $7.99/mo subscription
- Expose `purchaseAIPro()` method
- Expose `isAIProActive` boolean

##### [MODIFY] src/context/WorkoutContext.tsx

Add a "data source" abstraction:
- If `tier === 'ai_pro'` AND user is authenticated вҶ’ read/write to Convex
- Otherwise вҶ’ read/write to local AsyncStorage (existing behavior)
- This ensures the app works identically for Tier 1/2 users with zero changes

##### [MODIFY] AppNavigator.tsx

Add new screens:
- `AuthScreen` (modal presentation)
- `AIChatScreen` (in bottom tabs as a new "AI" tab, only visible for Tier 3)

##### [MODIFY] PaywallScreen.tsx

Add a second section below the $6.99 button:
- "Want AI Coaching? Upgrade to Pro for $7.99/mo"
- This button triggers the Auth flow first, then the subscription

